---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import NavBar from '../components/NavBar.astro';
import Twikoo from '../components/Twikoo.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="について - krya">
  <NavBar slot="header" />
  
  <div class="col-mb-12" id="main" role="main">
    <article class="post" data-pagefind-body>
      <h1 class="post-title" data-pagefind-meta="title">关于我</h1>
      <div class="post-content">

        <p>我居住成都🐼，目前处于创业阶段。</p>

        <p>积极尝试各种新技术，也喜欢听取一些新颖的观点。写这个博客是为了记录和分享自己的一些想法。</p>

        <p>写作频率不高。过去20年写了两三百篇，目前保留了一半左右，删除不少；因为随着成长，一些观念会逐渐改变。所以如果你看到我早期的文章言辞别扭，大可一笑而过，不必当真。</p>

        <h2>博客平台</h2>
        <p>2008 年开始写博客，那时候还在用百度空间。后来辗转网易博客、WordPress、Blogger，2014 年换到 Typecho，2026 年又把整个博客采用 Astro 框架静态化。工具一直在变，写的习惯没变——不定时更新一些旅行见闻、生活碎片，以及偶尔冒出来的想法。</p>

        <h2>写作方式</h2>
        <p>前端页面可能托管在 Vercel、Cloudflare 等托管平台；本地文章保存在家里的小主机上。平常用 Joplin 写文章（依靠 S3 全平台同步），用 Obsidian 编辑，然后让 Hermes 帮我推送到 GitHub。</p>

        <h2>About me</h2>

        <p>I'm based in <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chengdu">Chengdu</a>🐼, currently in the startup phase.</p>

        <p>I actively experiment with new technologies and enjoy exploring novel perspectives. I maintain this blog to record and share my thoughts.</p>

        <p>I don't write frequently. Over the past 20 years, I've written a couple of hundred posts, but only about half remain — I've deleted many as my views evolved over time. So if you come across my earlier writings and find the tone awkward, feel free to just laugh it off and don't take them seriously.</p>

        <h2>Blogging Platform</h2>
        <p>I started blogging in 2008 on Baidu Kongjian, then moved through Netease Blog, WordPress, and Blogger. In 2014, I switched to Typecho, and in 2026, I migrated the entire blog to a static site using the Astro framework. The tools keep changing, but the habit doesn't — I update this blog with travel notes, life fragments, and occasional thoughts whenever inspiration strikes.</p>

        <h2>Writing Workflow</h2>
        <p>The frontend is hosted on platforms like Vercel or Cloudflare; my articles are stored on a small home server. I typically write in Joplin (synced across all devices via S3), edit in Obsidian, and have Hermes push them to GitHub.</p>
        
        <h2>Contact:</h2>
        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:hi@krya.com">hi@krya.com</a> </p>
        <p>Twitter: <a href="https://x.com/uniifi">jin</a></p>
        
        <h2>版权声明</h2>
        <p>Unless otherwise noted, all content on this site/this article is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International License <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/">CC BY-NC-SA 4.0</a></p>
        <p>除另有注明外，本站/本文内容采用 知识共享署名 - 非商业性使用 - 相同方式共享 4.0 国际许可协议 (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0) 进行许可。</p>
      </div>
    </article>
    
    <Twikoo />
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
